  <brief_title>Effects of Inspiratory Muscle Training on Dyspnea in Subjects With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</brief_title>
  <acronym>IMT</acronym>
  <official_title>Effects of Inspiratory Muscle Training Combined With a Pulmonary Rehabilitation Program Versus a Program of Pulmonary Rehabilitation Alone on Dyspnea: a Randomized Trial</official_title>
